<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-15 14:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0294 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      11-15 1292
</HEADER>
<BODY>
 AM-NYT-BUDGET  
(gm) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; FOR TUESDAY AMs &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Here are today's top news stories from The New York Times News
Service for AMs of Tuesday, Nov. 16:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; CHINA-U.S. TRADE &LR;  (``i'' code)
</P>
<P>
