<P>
   Editors, papers that published the article LATIN-SCHOLAR, from
the New York Times Ideas Page, filed Friday for Saturday release
may wish to use the following correction:
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service story on Saturday about Ilan
Stavans, a Mexican scholar who has become an important figure in
Latino literature, incorrectly described the nationality of Octavio
Paz, the poet. He is Mexican, not Peruvian.
</P>
