<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL-PALESTINIANS (Jerusalem) will not move in tonight's New
York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Nov. 15.
</P>
</TEXT>
