of losing that advantage if it doesn't do more to encourage growth
in the technology sector, the California Council on Science and
Technology says in a report to be presented Tuesday in Los Angeles.
Government must help encourage tech growth by re-examining its tax
structure, educational system and government policies, the report
says. By Jason Cohen. (Will move on the ``f'' financial news wire.)
