should see major long-term gains from the breakthrough trade
US-China agreement, trade trackers said, although the improvements
will probably be gradual. For example, Hollywood will benefit from
the easing of heavy restrictions but the Chinese market will likely
remain riddled with pirated versions of U.S. movies. By Dave
McNary. (Will move on the ``f'' financial news wire.)
</P>
