<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-15 19:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0602 &Cx1f; tic-z
u v BC-AZR-BUDGET-AZR &LR;      11-15 0123
