<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-TRIVIA-Q&AMP;A-TEX </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The UNDATED story slugged TRIVIA-Q&AMP;A will not move in tonight's
Fort Worth Star-Telegram file for clients of the NYTimes News
Service. It is regularly budgeted to move on Tuesdays. &QL; 
</P>
