of the American Council on Exercise, a nonprofit group that reports
on fitness and certifies personal trainers and aerobic instructors.
``After clothing to cover your body, a heart-rate monitor is the
single most essential piece of fitness equipment,'' Florez says.
(Don Hogan Charles/New York Times Photo)
