<HEADLINE>
IT'S NO USE TRYING TO HERD BAPTISTS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service Clients) 
By PAUL HARRAL 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Reading about the Texas Baptists meeting in El Paso, Texas,
recently, I was reminded of a favorite Will Rogers quote: ``I
belong to no organized party. I am a Democrat.''
</P>
<P>
   Sometimes I feel that way: I belong to no organized
